column13: The invention is a composition for treatment of transplanted tumors in animals which is a mixture of the hydrogen bromide salts of bis-(beta-dichloroethyl)-hydrazides of cystine and cysteine, method of preparation therefor, and use thereof for treatment of transplanted tumors in animals.
